title: Dog Walking
text:
Currently, I offer dog walking / sitting in 2 ways:



Phoebe’s Paw Parade



Booking Link

These walk schedules are meant for longer term customers. You can start by booking an inital 1.5 hour walk at any available times on my Calendly. If your pup seems like a long term fit for the group, we can discuss booking at a weekly or monthly rate.





Rover
This is typically a good way to book a one time service. Since this is done through the platform, my prices are a bit higher to accounts for the 25% fee rover takes on all bookings. If you want to work something out long term after booking, we can discuss my non-Rover price points
Use this link to check out my profile and book, and use the promocode: JUSTIG74774 for $20 off your first walk.

title: Phoebe
text: One-pager with useful information about Phoebe! This includes shots she has included, her eating schedule / diet, general temperament, and hopefully some fun pictures / other data projects related to Phoebe I can think of.

title: Phoebe
text:
Health & Grooming
Health-wise, she is up to date on all her shots (reattaching medical records to this form). Back in November 2022, she had a little bout of Ghirardi. She hasn’t had issues since, but I have included the rest of her antibiotics (please text me poo photos if you need assistance). 
Grooming you shouldn’t have to worry about this at all. I gave her a nice bath yesterday (April 5th). She gets a bath once a week, so unless you notice extenuating circumstances, don’t feel pressured to bathe her.

title: Phoebe
text:
Poop / Pee Schedule
While Phoebe is not 100% potty-trained, here are some pointers: 
For poopies:  She typically will need to poop around 30 mins - 1 hour after eating a meal. This is when I typically take her on walks. 
* She also will do a VERY slow squatting motion. If you are fast, just yell “Good girl!, come with me!” and she will follow you to the best area before doing the deed

For pee-pees: I’m sorry, but I haven’t found the magic bullet here. If you discover any tricks that work to bring home, it would be greatly appreciated
